- I don't know. Like confused.

35:07.636 --> 35:09.900
Like human?

35:12.308 --> 35:14.970
Yeah, and I don't
wanna feel that way.

35:42.705 --> 35:44.639
- What's up?
- Nothin'.

35:44.707 --> 35:46.971
How's it goin'?

35:47.042 --> 35:49.033
It's fine.

35:50.479 --> 35:52.413
You all right?

35:53.849 --> 35:56.841
Yeah. Yeah.

35:58.554 --> 36:01.854
I just- I want you to know
that it's okay.

36:02.925 --> 36:04.893
I mean...

36:04.960 --> 36:08.362
you don't have to feel uncomfortable
if you and Kyle get back together.

36:09.965 --> 36:12.900
What?

36:12.968 --> 36:15.528
I saw you two together
here yesterday.

36:17.640 --> 36:20.405
Okay, um-

36:20.476 --> 36:24.379
Max, first of all, that couldn't be
further from what's happening.

36:24.446 --> 36:26.346
And secondly...

36:26.415 --> 36:29.783
ifit was happening, I wouldn't need
your permission, Max.

36:31.620 --> 36:34.920
- I'm getting out of here. You sound like Isabel.
- Why do I sound like Isabel?

36:34.990 --> 36:37.550
She's got this thing all of a sudden
that I'm controlling.

36:37.626 --> 36:39.754
- Oh, so it's her thing.
- What?

36:39.828 --> 36:43.059
Max,just take a psych class,
because you are controlling.

36:43.132 --> 36:48.298
Hey, I am who I am. I've got a lot going
on, and I'm trying to make things work.

36:48.370 --> 36:51.431
Max, you know what
your problem is?

36:51.507 --> 36:54.499
You put everything on yourself-
on your own shoulders.

36:56.679 --> 36:59.273
Maybe you should have some faith
in the people around you.

37:14.396 --> 37:17.593
- I thought you might be here.
- Max.

37:17.666 --> 37:20.158
<i>Oh, honey, sit down.</i>

37:20.235 --> 37:22.226
I'm glad you're here.

37:22.304 --> 37:24.500
I've been wanting
to talk to you about...

37:25.708 --> 37:27.767
something we've never
discussed before.

37:31.013 --> 37:33.482
Have you ever thought about
trying to find your--

37:33.549 --> 37:35.813
your real parents?

37:35.884 --> 37:38.581
I mean, because
I've been thinking.

37:38.654 --> 37:42.181
I mean, maybe there's a reason
whyyou can't talk to me.

37:42.257 --> 37:44.419
Maybe you need
real parents for that.

37:44.493 --> 37:47.986
Maybe your father and I
just... aren't enough for you.

37:49.832 --> 37:52.631
Mom, I don't think
we'll ever find our real parents.

37:53.702 --> 37:56.433
And... maybe it would,
you know...

37:57.506 --> 37:59.497
give us some answers, but...

38:01.610 --> 38:03.601
please don't ever think
that you're not enough.

38:05.914 --> 38:07.939
I mean...

38:08.016 --> 38:09.950
without you, I-l-

38:10.018 --> 38:12.783
I don't know
where I would even be.

38:14.857 --> 38:18.225
Max, nothing you are...

38:18.293 --> 38:20.352
could ever
turn me away from you.

38:20.429 --> 38:22.830
I mean...

38:22.898 --> 38:24.889
I love you.

38:24.967 --> 38:27.493
And you're my son.

38:27.569 --> 38:29.560
Do you understand that?

38:31.607 --> 38:33.200
Yeah.

38:33.275 --> 38:35.869
Then why-

38:35.944 --> 38:38.140
why can't you
just tell me your secret?

38:47.589 --> 38:49.990
This is for you.

38:50.058 --> 38:52.186
- Sorry for the wrapping.
- [Chuckles]

38:54.363 --> 38:56.354
Oh.

38:57.499 --> 38:59.490
Your house.

39:01.603 --> 39:05.198
I remember my first few nights
in our house so well.

39:05.274 --> 39:07.606
[Sighs]
I hated it so much.

39:09.444 --> 39:11.435
For Isabel
it was different.

39:12.614 --> 39:14.605
She saw you and Dad...

39:14.683 --> 39:17.846
and from the very first moment,
she knew she was home.

39:20.455 --> 39:23.186
And I would lie in my bed
all night and cry.

39:25.127 --> 39:27.186
Because you wanted
to go home.

39:29.464 --> 39:31.455
Yeah.

39:34.536 --> 39:36.527
And you gave me this.

39:37.673 --> 39:39.903
And you said that
it was a magic house...

39:41.243 --> 39:44.304
and that if I held on to it,
it would take me home.

39:46.181 --> 39:48.843
But the thing is,
it would never bring me home...

39:50.152 --> 39:52.211
because I don't know
where home is.

39:54.122 --> 39:56.250
I don't remember.

39:56.325 --> 39:59.522
<i>That's the truth.</i>

39:59.595 --> 40:01.996
And if you can't accept that,
then I understand.

40:04.233 --> 40:07.225
-I could leave.
- Leave? Max, please-

40:07.302 --> 40:10.897
Mom, don't ask me
about this anymore.

40:10.973 --> 40:13.169
It's nothing bad.
It's nothing dangerous.

40:13.242 --> 40:15.939
<i>I beg you to trust me.</i>

40:17.312 --> 40:21.010
I mean, you're my mother.

40:25.220 --> 40:27.655
Please, Mom.

