41:40.595 --> 41:42.791
I'm sorry.

41:42.864 --> 41:46.300
I just- I just wanted her to know.

41:48.103 --> 41:50.265
I wanted it so bad.

41:51.907 --> 41:53.841
I know.

41:55.077 --> 41:57.239
- I know you did.
- [ Crying]

42:01.616 --> 42:03.948
We have each other.

